Shortcut keys: 
//For project
- cmd + R - build and run project 
- cmd + B - build project 
- cmd + shift + K - clean project 
- cmd + . - stop execution

//Code work 
- cmd + / - comment/uncomment selected lines of code 
- cmd + ] or [ - change intendation on one Tab 
- ctrl + i - change structure of code to fit guideline
- cmd + j - open assistant editor 

//Project navigation
- cmd + shift + O - find and open File in projects
- ctrl + 6 - open file navigator
- cmd + number[1 -7] change active tab of left navigation
- cmd + 0 - hide left panel
- cmd + alt + 0 - hide right panel  

//Project search 
- cmd + shift + F - global search

//Refactoring 
- cmd + ctrl + E - rename everything to one name
